Alan M. Watson (UNAM), Nat Butler (ASU), Alexander Kutyrev (GSFC), William 
H. Lee (UNAM), Michael G. Richer (UNAM), Ori Fox (UCB), J. Xavier 
Prochaska (UCSC), Josh Bloom (UCB), Antonino Cucchiara (ORAU/GSFC), 
